{
  "texts": [
    "We then further assist the models on puzzles they initially fail to solve by allowing three additional attempts per level Figure 1: Example of our 8-puzzle evaluation pipeline.",
    "The model receives the system prompt, in this case, our Zero-Shot prompt, as well as the puzzle.",
    "The model then returns a sequence of moves.",
    "An external function applies each move to determine whether the model solved the puzzle.",
    "We highlight the legal moves in green."
  ]
}